{"tid":1273743,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"G20與71遊行, 前後陰謀論(講故)","createTime":"2019-07-01T14:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T14:46:01.000Z","uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1fef76395b1e0ed10969c56e8e4e0890361aed6d","tid":1273743,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:46:01.000Z","msg":"簡單講故事 =&gt; 習近平在忙於G20, 有人假傳聖旨,要777武力震懾示威者.<br />\n所以777 28號見警方間接落order同做好劇本.<br />\n6月30日借支持警察集會激怒示威者<br />\n同日在71前大動作去激怒激怒示威者, 相關組織同議員.<br />\n而習近平29日收到風,同特朗普傾完即閃.吾理下午同巴西總統會面.<br />\n因收到風, 有人想借殺示威者去將責任推給佢,整佢下台.<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞=&gt;<br />\n1) G20 28 號開始<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/345721/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E8%A6%8B%E5%9B%9B%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E8%81%B7%E6%96%B9%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8-%E6%96%A5%E6%9C%89%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E5%88%BB%E6%84%8F%E6%8C%91%E9%87%81%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F345721%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%259B%259B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%25E8%2581%25B7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8-%25E6%2596%25A5%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2588%25BB%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%258C%2591%25E9%2587%2581%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9&d=d%2FCPXFTd5ssE%2Fv2vqbbCu85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=a95d4b95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/345721/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E8%A6%8B%E5%9B%9B%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E8%81%B7%E6%96%B9%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8-%E6%96%A5%E6%9C%89%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E5%88%BB%E6%84%8F%E6%8C%91%E9%87%81%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9</a><br />\n<br />\n2) 林鄭月娥見四警隊職方代表 斥有示威者刻意挑釁警方<br />\n<br />\n有可能當日林鄭月娥用28, 29 call 馬, 統籌撐警集會,<br />\n定下其方向.( 方向可以激烈, 溫和, 或兩者之間 )<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.soundofhope.org/gb/2019/06/30/n2997991.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.soundofhope.org%2Fgb%2F2019%2F06%2F30%2Fn2997991.html&d=d%2FCPXFTd5ssE%2Fv2vqbbCu85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=1cf0d322\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.soundofhope.org/gb/2019/06/30/n2997991.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2a) 1 美国总统川普通过自媒体披露更多川习会详情<br />\n川普与习近平上周六（29日）举行峰会。川普第二天，星期天早上，<br />\n通过自媒体推特，进一步披露川习会谈的详情。<br />\n<br />\n2b) 中国代表团迟到过久 巴西总统取消与习近平会谈<br />\n巴西总统波索纳洛与中国领导人习近平，原定在日本大坂举行的二十国首脑峰会期间进行会谈。<br />\n但因中方迟到太久，巴西方面取消了这次会谈。请听报导。<br />\n<br />\n=&gt; 傳言當日下即飛回中國, 可能因中國內部出事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dotdotnews.com/2019/06/30/videos/%E7%8F%BE%E8%BA%AB%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83-%E8%AD%9A%E6%83%A0%E7%8F%A0%EF%BC%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%80%E5%84%AA%E7%A7%80%E7%9A%84%E9%9A%8A%E4%BC%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dotdotnews.com%2F2019%2F06%2F30%2Fvideos%2F%25E7%258F%25BE%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E6%2592%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583-%25E8%25AD%259A%25E6%2583%25A0%25E7%258F%25A0%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%2584%25AA%25E7%25A7%2580%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%259A%258A%25E4%25BC%258D&d=d%2FCPXFTd5ssE%2Fv2vqbbCu85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=2732028d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dotdotnews.com/2019/06/30/videos/%E7%8F%BE%E8%BA%AB%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83-%E8%AD%9A%E6%83%A0%E7%8F%A0%EF%BC%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%80%E5%84%AA%E7%A7%80%E7%9A%84%E9%9A%8A%E4%BC%8D</a><br />\n撐警集會<br />\n<br />\n3) 撐警集會言論相當激烈, 應該明天就係71遊行, 點解個日仲激怒D示威人士???<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而6月30日中午到夜晚, 疑似有人派人四出攪事<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E9%9B%BB%E5%8F%B0%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%8B%E8%99%95%E9%81%AD%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%AA%E9%9D%A2%E7%94%B7%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E-%E5%8F%B0%E9%95%B7-%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2596%2593%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%258F%25B0%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%2599%2595%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25B9%25AA%25E9%259D%25A2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A3%259E-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%2581%2590%25E5%259A%2587%2F&d=d%2FCPXFTd5ssE%2Fv2vqbbCu85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=bc03c104\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2596%2593%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%258F%25B0%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%2599%2595%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25B9%25AA%25E9%259D%25A2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A3%259E-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%2581%2590%25E5%259A%2587%2F&h=46284125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E9%9B%BB%E5%8F%B0%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%8B%E8%99%95%E9%81%AD%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%AA%E9%9D%A2%E7%94%B7%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E-%E5%8F%B0%E9%95%B7-%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87/</a><br />\n<br />\n4)民間電台辦事處遭四幪面男破壞 台長：政治恐嚇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9C%89%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%A8%B1%E5%B7%B2%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%A5%BD%E7%82%BA%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E8%B2%A0%E8%B2%AC-063054771.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25A1%259D%25E6%2593%258A%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E8%25B2%25AC-063054771.html&d=d%2FCPXFTd5ssE%2Fv2vqbbCu85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=ca8e71b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9C%89%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%A8%B1%E5%B7%B2%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%A5%BD%E7%82%BA%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E8%B2%A0%E8%B2%AC-063054771.html</a><br />\n<br />\n5) 有衝擊立法會示威者稱已準備好為行動負責<br />\n<br />\n7月1日 1pm 左右衝擊立法會, 而差不多時間警方要求取消7日遊行<br />\n在衝擊立法會其間,點解無用速龍同催(驅散示威者)<br />\n<br />\n有傳言777 想武力震懾"}]}